Runtime Control Loop

The system operates continuously in a feedback loop.

Observe → Interpret → Translate → Simulate → Render → Observe

Expanded form:

User command
    ↓
Director Agent interprets intent
    ↓
Pantheon validation layer checks invariants
    ↓
Neural–Spatial Bridge compiles meaning
    ↓
Simulation runtime updates world state
    ↓
Renderer produces perceptual output
    ↓
User observes updated world

The cycle repeats in real time.

